name: Patanjali Wheat Daliya
description: Patanjali Wheat Daliya is made from high-quality wheat grains that are broken down into smaller fragments. It is highly nutritious and an excellent source of fiber, which aids digestion. This daliya is perfect for making a wholesome breakfast porridge or a savory khichdi with vegetables. It is processed to ensure cleanliness and uniformity. Patanjali Daliya is low in fat and cholesterol, making it heart-healthy. It provides a feeling of fullness, preventing overeating and helping in weight management.

name: Organic Tattva Wheat Daliya
description: Organic Tattva Wheat Daliya is certified organic, ensuring it is free from pesticides and synthetic fertilizers. It retains the natural bran and germ of the wheat, providing maximum nutrition. Rich in complex carbohydrates, it releases energy slowly, keeping you active throughout the day. It has a nutty flavor and a chewy texture when cooked. Ideal for health-conscious families who prefer organic produce. Use it to make a sweet lapsi or a nutritious salad.

name: Safe Harvest Pearl Millet (Bajra)
description: Safe Harvest Pearl Millet (Bajra) is a gluten-free ancient grain that is packed with iron, magnesium, and protein. Sourced from pesticide-free farms, it is a great alternative to rice or wheat. Bajra is known for its heat-generating properties, making it ideal for consumption in winters. It can be ground into flour for rotis or cooked whole like rice. It helps in controlling blood sugar levels and is beneficial for heart health. A traditional superfood for the modern diet.

name: Manna Ragi Malt
description: Manna Ragi Malt is a sprouted finger millet flour that serves as a complete health drink for the whole family. Sprouting ragi increases its calcium and iron bioavailability, making it easier to absorb. It is a natural source of Vitamin D and protein. This malt can be cooked with milk or water to make a nutritious porridge. It is excellent for growing children and elderly people for bone health. No artificial colors or preservatives are added.

name: India Gate Quinoa
description: India Gate Quinoa is a premium quality superfood that is a complete protein source, containing all nine essential amino acids. It is gluten-free, high in fiber, and has a low glycemic index. This quinoa is pre-washed to remove the bitter saponin coating, making it ready to cook. It cooks up fluffy and light with a delicate crunch. Use it as a rice replacement, in salads, or for making healthy burger patties. It is an excellent choice for vegans and weight watchers.

name: Yoga Bar 20g Protein Bar (Chocolate Brownie)
description: Yoga Bar 20g Protein Bar in Chocolate Brownie flavor is the ultimate post-workout snack. Packed with 20g of high-quality whey and almond protein, it helps in muscle recovery and growth. It contains no soy, no gluten, and no added preservatives. The rich chocolate taste comes from real cocoa, making it feel like a cheat meal while being healthy. It is also loaded with fiber and essential vitamins. Perfect for athletes and fitness enthusiasts on the go.

name: RiteBite Max Protein Active (Choco Slim)
description: RiteBite Max Protein Active bar offers 20g of protein and is designed to fuel your active lifestyle. The Choco Slim flavor is sugar-free and 100% vegetarian. It contains a blend of whey, soy, and casein protein for sustained energy release. Enriched with 21 vitamins and minerals, electrolytes, and omega-3, it is more than just a protein bar—it's a complete meal replacement. It satisfies hunger cravings for up to 4 hours. Great for busy professionals and trekkers.

name: The Whole Truth - Peanut Butter Protein Bar
description: The Whole Truth Protein Bars are famous for their clean label—ingredients you can read and understand. The Peanut Butter bar is made with just peanuts, dates, and whey protein. No added sugar, no artificial sweeteners, no gluten, and no soy. It offers a dense, chewy texture with the authentic taste of roasted peanuts. Each bar provides 15g of protein. It represents honest food marketing and delivers pure nutrition without the junk.

name: Monkey Bar Vegan Energy Bar (Dark Cocoa & Hazelnut)
description: Monkey Bar offers a delicious vegan energy bar made with dark cocoa and premium hazelnuts. It is a natural energy booster made from fruits, nuts, and seeds. Free from added sugar and processed additives, it relies on dates for sweetness. The crunchy hazelnuts paired with intense dark chocolate make it a delightful treat. Ideal for a mid-day slump or a pre-run snack. It is gluten-free and dairy-free, catering to specific dietary requirements.

name: Kellogg's K-Energy Bar (Choco & Nut)
description: Kellogg's K-Energy Bar is a tasty blend of cereal grains, chocolates, and nuts. It provides a quick burst of energy and is perfect for beating hunger pangs between meals. The bar has a crispy texture thanks to the rice crispies and rolled oats. The chocolate coating makes it appealing to children. It is fortified with essential B-group vitamins. A convenient pocket-sized snack that you can carry to school, college, or work.

name: Amul Kool Cafe
description: Amul Kool Cafe is a refreshing milk and coffee blend that energizes you instantly. Made from fresh Amul milk and premium coffee, it offers a smooth and creamy taste. It is best enjoyed chilled and is a perfect companion for hot summer days. The can packaging makes it easy to carry and consume on the go. It provides calcium and protein from milk along with the kick of caffeine. A favorite among youth and coffee lovers across India.

name: Cavin's Strawberry Milkshake
description: Cavin's Strawberry Milkshake is a thick and creamy delight loved by kids. It combines the goodness of double-toned milk with the sweet and tangy flavor of strawberries. Enriched with Zinc, Vitamin A, and Vitamin D, it supports immunity and bone health. The UHT treatment ensures a long shelf life without preservatives. It is a great lunchbox addition or an after-school treat. The convenient tetra pack with a straw makes it mess-free and easy to drink.

name: Amul Rose Lassi
description: Amul Rose Lassi is a traditional refreshing drink made from pasteurized toned milk dahi. It is flavored with rose syrup, giving it a fragrant and cooling effect. The lassi is rich in calcium and probiotics, aiding digestion and gut health. It has a perfect balance of sweetness and tanginess. The tetra pack ensures freshness and hygiene. Ideal for consuming after a spicy meal or as a hydrating summer drink. It brings the taste of authentic Indian lassi to your home.

name: Hershey's Milkshake - Chocolate
description: Hershey's Milkshake brings the classic taste of Hershey's chocolate in a liquid form. It contains 30% more calcium than regular cow's milk and is fortified with essential vitamins and minerals. The rich, velvety chocolate flavor creates a premium drinking experience. It serves as a great breakfast accompaniment or a midnight snack. Both hot and cold consumption is possible, though it tastes best when chilled. A treat for chocolate connoisseurs of all ages.

name: Paper Boat Thandai
description: Paper Boat Thandai is a nostalgic drink that captures the essence of Indian festivals like Holi. It is a milk-based drink infused with a rich paste of almonds, fennel seeds, melon seeds, pepper, and cardamom. It contains no preservatives or added colors. The flavor is intense, creamy, and cooling. It serves as a great energy booster and aids in digestion due to the spices. Packaged in Paper Boat's signature pouches, it is easy to sip and savour memories.

name: MTR Rava Idli Mix
description: MTR Rava Idli Mix is the easiest way to make fluffy, soft, and delicious Rava Idlis at home. A signature product from MTR, it contains semolina, cashew nuts, and aromatic spices tempered in ghee. You just need to add curd, mix, and steam. It saves the hassle of soaking and grinding batter. Perfect for a quick, healthy, and filling breakfast. Serve it with coconut chutney and sambar for a complete South Indian meal experience.

name: Gits Dosai Mix
description: Gits Dosai Mix allows you to prepare crispy and golden dosas instantly. Made from high-quality rice and lentil flour, it undergoes a natural fermentation process before being dehydrated, ensuring the authentic sour taste of dosa batter. It is 100% vegetarian and free from artificial flavors and colors. Simply add water to the mix and your batter is ready. Ideal for making plain dosas, masala dosas, or uttapams. A consistent and convenient solution for dosa lovers.

name: Tata Sampann Multigrain Chilla Mix
description: Tata Sampann Multigrain Chilla Mix is a nutritious breakfast option packed with the goodness of pulses and grains. It contains moong dal, oats, brown rice, and spices. Developed with Chef Sanjeev Kapoor, it ensures a perfect balance of taste and health. It is high in protein and fiber, making it great for weight management. The mix is ready to cook in 15 minutes. You can add chopped vegetables to the batter to make it even more wholesome.

name: Betty Crocker Pancake Mix (Classic)
description: Betty Crocker Pancake Mix brings the fluffy American-style pancakes to your kitchen. It is incredibly easy to use—just add water or milk to the mix, whisk, and cook. The result is light, airy, and golden pancakes. It serves as a blank canvas for toppings like maple syrup, honey, fresh fruits, or whipped cream. Kids love it for breakfast or as an evening snack. It delivers a consistent taste and texture that Betty Crocker is globally known for.

name: Aashirvaad Instant Veggie Upma Mix
description: Aashirvaad Instant Veggie Upma Mix is a comfort food that is ready in minutes. It is loaded with dehydrated vegetables like carrots, peas, and onions, along with roasted semolina and authentic spices. You just need to add boiling water and let it sit. It tastes like homemade upma with the aroma of curry leaves and mustard seeds. No cooking is required, making it perfect for travel or hostel students. It is wholesome, tasty, and convenient.

name: Dabur Honey
description: Dabur Honey is India's most trusted honey brand, sourced from the finest hives in the Himalayas and Sunderbans. It is 100% pure and passes stringent NMR testing to ensure no added sugar. Known for its rich taste and distinct aroma, it is a great natural sweetener. It helps in weight management when consumed with warm water and lemon. It is also a natural cough suppressant and boosts immunity. Use it in tea, on toast, or as a topping for desserts.

name: Dabur Chyawanprash
description: Dabur Chyawanprash is a time-tested Ayurvedic formulation made from over 40 potent herbs, with Amla as the main ingredient. It is scientifically proven to double immunity and protect against common illnesses like cold and cough. It boosts energy and strength, suitable for all age groups. The sweet and spicy taste is loved by many. Consuming a spoonful daily helps build resistance against infections and improves respiratory health. It is a daily health supplement for the entire family.

name: Saffola Honey
description: Saffola Honey is 100% pure and NMR tested, guaranteeing no sugar adulteration. It is sourced from antibiotic-free beehives. Saffola Honey is rich in antioxidants and helps boost metabolism. It has a smooth texture and a delightful golden color. It is a healthier alternative to refined sugar for your beverages and desserts. The squeezy bottle packaging ensures zero mess and easy usage. A pure and natural product for health-conscious consumers.

name: Baidyanath Chyawanprash Special
description: Baidyanath Chyawanprash Special is prepared according to the traditional Ayurvedic recipe. It is rich in Vitamin C from fresh Amlas and contains 52 essential herbs. It helps strengthen the body's internal defense mechanism and revitalizes the system. It is excellent for improving digestion and respiratory function. The inclusion of real silver foil (varak) and saffron adds to its rejuvenating properties. It is an excellent anti-aging supplement that promotes youthful vigor.

name: Organic India Honey
description: Organic India Honey is certified organic wild forest honey. It is collected from the Himalayan forests where the bees feed on organic flora. It is unfiltered and unpasteurized, retaining natural enzymes, pollen, and nutrients. It has a robust, distinct flavor that is different from commercial farm honey. It is a rich source of energy and heals wounds and burns due to its antibacterial properties. Perfect for those who seek honey in its most natural and raw form.

name: Prasuma Chicken Salami (Plain)
description: Prasuma Chicken Salami is a premium deli meat made from high-quality chicken breast meat. It is lightly seasoned to bring out the natural flavors of the meat. Pre-sliced for convenience, it is ready to eat right out of the pack or can be lightly pan-fried. Perfect for sandwiches, pizzas, and salads. It is free from antibiotics and hormones. The texture is tender and succulent, making it a favorite for breakfast platters or cold cuts.

name: Zorabian Chicken Sausages (Spicy)
description: Zorabian Chicken Sausages are made from farm-fresh chicken and a special blend of spicy herbs. They are juicy, flavorful, and free from MSG and added colors. These sausages are pre-cooked and only need to be grilled or shallow fried for a few minutes. They add a spicy kick to your breakfast or hot dogs. Zorabian ensures high hygiene standards and antibiotic-free meat. A great source of lean protein for meat lovers.

name: Licious Chicken Lyoner (Classic)
description: Licious Chicken Lyoner is a classic breakfast cold cut. It is finely minced chicken meat mixed with subtle spices, steam-cooked to perfection. It has a smooth texture and cuts easily. Ideal for making club sandwiches or serving with cheese and crackers. Licious ensures the meat is fresh and never frozen, vacuum packed to retain freshness. It contains no artificial preservatives. A versatile ingredient for quick and protein-rich snacks.

name: Venky's Chicken Frankfurters
description: Venky's Chicken Frankfurters are classic hot dog sausages made from tender chicken meat. They are smoked to give a distinct aroma and flavor. Soft and juicy, they are a hit with children. Boil, grill, or fry them and serve in a bun with mustard and ketchup. Venky's is a pioneer in the Indian poultry industry, ensuring safe and quality products. These franks are a convenient option for quick meals and parties.

name: Meatzaa Chicken Ham Slices
description: Meatzaa Chicken Ham Slices offer the taste of traditional ham with the lean benefits of chicken. The slices are cured and cooked, offering a salty and savory flavor profile. They are low in fat compared to pork ham. Use them in sandwiches, wraps, or chop them up for salads and omelets. Meatzaa products are processed in state-of-the-art facilities. A delicious way to add protein to your diet without the hassle of cooking meat from scratch.
